quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  4,66,"So tawno min parluno e ma…ď…ďe won de : "mbaree pittaali mon …óin", maa "njalton e galleeji mon", …ďe mb…óataano …óum si wanaa see…óaa e ma…ď…ďe. Sinno kam…ďe …ďe mba…óno kon ko …ďe mbaajoranoo, …óum laatotono mo∆ī∆īere wonan de …ďe, …ďura tii…óude kadi tabital :"
  4,67,"Nden tuma, min ngokkatno…ďe immorde ka amen, njo…ďdi mawndi,"
  4,68,"Min pewno …ďe laawol po∆īcingol."
  4,69,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo on : …ďeen …óoon ngondoyta …ďeen …ďe Alla wa…ói dookem dowe muen gila e annabaa…ďe, ha e goongu…ďe, e sahiddinnoo…ďe, e mo∆ī∆īube. ∆Āen …óon mo∆ī∆īii wonndii…ďe !"
  4,70,"Ngal …óon ∆Āural ko immorde ka Alla, Alla Yonii ganndu…óo !"
  4,71,"Ee hey mon gooŇč…óin…ďe, njogitee deentor…ói mon …óin, ndunnjon ko on seertu…ďe maa runnjon on rentu…ďe."
  4,72,"Hino e mon nee…ďnotoo…ďe, si musiiba he…ďii on, o wi'a : "GooŇč…óii Alla Neeminii e am, nde tawnoo mi mi wone daano e ma…ď…ď e ceedii…óo ! "."
  4,73,"Si tawii he…ďii on …ďural immorde ka Alla, ma o wi'a waona si tawii mee…óaa laataade hakkunde mon gi…óli: "Ee jalla am si mi tawdano e ma…ď…ďe ! mi malee malal manngal !"."
  4,74,"Yo ha…ďe fii laawol Alla ngol, …ďen …ďe no soottira nguurdam aduna …óam laakara on ! Kala on ka…ďaa…óo fii laawol Alla ngol o waraa maa o fooli, arma min ngokku mo njo…ďdi mawndi."